name: Lost and Confused
description:
#19
I made this piece when I was desperate about my artistic future.
No inspirations. I didn't know what to create, and I was frustrated, lost, and confused. Then, I connected with the feeling. So I found again what to draw: this piece.
 
2048x2048 mp4 video in a loop of 10 seconds

Piece #19 of the collection: I'm not your therapist but I'd like to cheer you up with my dorky art The series focuses on the fragility of the inner world and brings up topics that we often find in our long journey on earth.
